posting_body: ['Close to Campus!', 'Where Modern Denver Living Meets Comfort', 'Call Now:', 'show contact info', 'Bear Valley Park', '5775 W Dartmouth Ave, Denver, CO, 80227', 'Want more info on this unit?', 'See the link (below):', '<URL>', 'This is a 1 Bedroom, 1 Bath', 'Say hello to Bear Valley Park, a mecca for fun and adventure with a twist of modern comfort.', 'Our Denver, CO, apartments for rent sit in the center of an unbeatable location – close to scenic hiking and biking trails and just minutes from all your daily needs.', 'Garden-style grounds welcome you home each day, while phenomenal features and community amenities allow for a life of style and ease.', 'Let us be the first to welcome you to the Southwest Bear Valley Park neighborhood.', 'Features', '- In-Home Washer & Dryer', '- Stainless-Steel Appliances', '- Dishwasher', '- Walk-In Closets*', '- Gas Fireplace*', '- Air Conditioning', '- Kitchen Islands*', '- Spacious Private Balcony or Patio', '- Refrigerator with Ice Maker', '- Vaulted Ceilings*', '- Microwave', '*In Select Homes', 'Community Amenities', '- Parking Lot with Available Garages', '- 24-Hour Fitness Center', '- Bark Park', '- Heated Swimming Pool', '- Great Location Off Highway 285', '- Easy Access to Hiking & Biking Trails', '- Business Center', '- Outdoor Fire Pit', '- Clubhouse', '- Community BBQ Grills', '- Onsite Maintenance', 'Office Hours', 'Monday-Friday:10:00AM-6:00PM', 'Saturday:10:00AM-5:00PM', 'Prices are subject to change, based on availability and qualification of the applicant, additional fees may apply.', '5Y1bWKBQWt']
